>\n<br />\n件貨有壞(0.1)-&gt;個檢驗員有冇錯?<br />\n冇(0.95)-&gt;不通過 <br />\n<br />\n件貨冇壞(0.9)-&gt;個檢驗員有冇錯?<br />\n有(0.05)-&gt;不通過<br />\n<br />\n件貨冇壞0.9)-&gt;個檢驗員有冇錯?<br />\n冇(0.95)-&gt;通過(0.855)<br />\n<br />\n因為件貨有冇壞同檢驗員有冇錯兩件事係獨立，所以可以就咁乘<br />\n最後就將所有結果為&ldquo;通過&rdquo;既機率加曬佢: 0.005+0.855=0.86"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌明晒"},{"pid":"1e81de3da16f30b9636dab24577efcc762246062","tid":2218142,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"90%x95%+10%x5%<br />\n=86%  <br />\n~85%"},{"pid":"180f7e9bd732d068a5abafdcca8bc66c0cd4d551","tid":2218142,"uid":301258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"假設整100個鐘<br />\n<br />\n10%不良= 10個垃圾鐘（不通過）+90個好鐘（通過）<br />\n<br />\n誤判率5%   <br />\n<br />\n即係10個垃圾鐘入面，有5%誤判（即係垃圾當好）   10乘 0.05 （即係5%）被當係好鐘<br />\n=0.5 個好鐘<br />\n<br />\n而90個好鐘，5%誤判（好鐘被當成垃圾鐘）<br />\n90乘0.05= 4.5 個被當成壞鐘<br />\n90個好鐘 減 4.5個誤判 = 85.5 個好鐘<br />\n［如果你思考得快啲，直接90乘0.95就ok，因為95%冇誤判］<br />\n<br />\n然後，0.5 個+85.5 個= 86 個好鐘<br />\n100個鐘入面，86個鐘係好，即係86%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n答案係B（因為85%最接近86%，而題目要求選擇「最接近」）<br />\n應該夠清晰啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申數學拎F"},{"pid":"8b38421442bbb61d09480a86e4f1891d5243e30f","tid":2218142,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"連登成班中學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"